This October, 
We expanded our platform outside Mumbai for the very first time. 
We brought Ahmedabad the best of India’s homegrown streetwear brands, music and art. 
Here’s a rerun of experiences that were curated for you. 
Presenting to you : All You Can Street, Ahmedabad.

Media Partner : @gajaakriti 

#ahmedabad #aycs #allyoucanstreet #festival #art #streetwear #culture

3 days of fun, music, culture, and loads of cheer! - AYCS was a complete blast, thanks to everyone who tried something new for the first time and became a part of this chapter of #DoWhatFloatsYourboAt 🤜🤛

We had a blast with @Instagram at the All You Can Street Fest 2022. AYCS folks and their friends had a tremendous time creating cool, stunning and inspiring reels with the tools at the experience! Lots of happy faces and lots of memories for the books. Until next time, always remember to #ReelYourKicks! 

For those of you who missed it, here's a sneak peek into what went down

#ReelYourKicks #AllYouCanStreet #InstagramIndia
